  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators aim to study the specific elastance in ALI/ARDS patients during invasive
      mechanical ventilation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In sedated and paralyzed ALI/ARDS patients, we studied the specific elastance and also, we
      compared the specific elastance to healthy subjects during invasive mechanical ventilation.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
